cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

This paper is about optimizing neural network architectures for image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses learning curve extrapolation, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and the experiments involve image classification benchmarks, which could also fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
